# MAK Realty - Blockchain Real Estate Platform

**The Future of Real Estate Transactions**

---

## 🌟 About MAK Realty

MAK Realty is pioneering blockchain-powered real estate technology with AI recommendations and integrated financial services. Founded by **Michael Kelczewski**, a triple-licensed professional (Real Estate Broker + MLO + Insurance) with proven blockchain innovation.

### 🏆 Industry Firsts
- **First East Coast blockchain property recording** (2024)
- **Proven Bitcoin real estate transactions** ($1.75M+ deals)
- **Media recognition** in Delaware Business Times and Fox News
- **Triple-licensed expertise** in Real Estate, Mortgage, and Insurance

---

## 🚀 Platform Features

### 🔍 AI-Powered Property Search
- Smart recommendations based on user behavior
- Real-time MLS integration
- Advanced filtering and favorites system

### 💰 Blockchain Mortgage Calculator
- Cryptocurrency payment integration (Bitcoin, Ethereum, USDC)
- Real-time pre-qualification assessment
- Transparent blockchain transaction recording

### 🛡️ Insurance Integration Platform
- Multi-carrier quote comparison
- Bundle optimization (Auto + Home + Life)
- Real-time pricing from major insurers

### 📊 Professional Agent Dashboard
- Unified lead management system
- AI-powered lead scoring
- Transaction pipeline tracking

---

## 💡 Innovation Highlights

**Blockchain Transparency**: Every transaction recorded on immutable blockchain ledger for unprecedented trust and transparency.

**AI-Driven Intelligence**: Machine learning algorithms analyze user behavior for personalized property recommendations.

**Integrated Services**: Complete Real Estate + Mortgage + Insurance solution in one platform.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React 18, Tailwind CSS, Lucide Icons
- **Blockchain**: Ethereum, Smart Contracts, Web3.js
- **APIs**: MLS Integration, Crypto Exchanges, Insurance Carriers
- **AI/ML**: Property Recommendation Engine, Lead Scoring

